data.description: Inviting, 4 Bedroom, 3 bath home located on a spacious .68 acre cul-de-sac lot in the Oak Hill development in Barnegat features hardwood flooring, cherry kitchen cabinetry, granite counter tops, fireplace, 2 car garage, full basement, 3 year old furnace and central air, large deck, expanded laundry room and much more! Convenient location close to schools, shopping, Garden State Parkway, Barnegat Township Bay Beach and L.B.I. beaches. Enjoy area festivals, concerts in the parks, entertainment at the Public Dock, sandy beaches, local seafood restaurants and everything else that the Jersey Shore has to offer!
